This snapshot shows that once the scrollbar appears, `S-down` scrolls the
preview content by one line.

    :k S-down
    :snap "/\d{4}-\d{2}-\d{2} \d{2}:\d{2}:\d{1,2}/t" "/(?:@|○|◆)\s+([a-z]{8})/w" "/\b([0-9a-f]{8})\b/h"

